    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar </strong>and cook for 6-7 min or until softened and starting to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
