            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until tender</p><p>Once tender, add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and cook for 10-15 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1600.-step-4-x200.jpg",
