            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>haddock bites </strong>(unevenly sized haddock bites? Chop any larger ones into bite-sized pieces!) to the pan and cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until the fish is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> Spanish-style haddock stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
