    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>garlic & parsley flatbreads</strong> into quarters</p><p>Serve the <strong>Spanish-style haddock stew</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped parsley</strong> and the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic & parsley flatbreads </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
